Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到在這鎮上會遇到布蘭登
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.90,0:01:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝上帝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.64,0:01:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然想盡方法要跟你取得聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.90,0:02:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.67,0:02:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管看到你身陷險境
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.26,0:02:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻什麼都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我…對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.62,0:02:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 瑪麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.33,0:02:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.59,0:02:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗亞在這鎮上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.38,0:02:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈利也在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我自己也在這裡生活著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.39,0:02:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是我的居所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因為這樣 就讓我滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.53,0:02:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道保護重要的人是多麼困難的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.26,0:02:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是單純的滿足著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:03:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Daddy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.86,0:03:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好氣派的遲到啊 布蘭登
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.81,0:03:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會"不是"吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣沉默寡言又幼稚的傢伙居然也有對象嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的對你刮目相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.11,0:03:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢在我之前成家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非殺了你不可
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.06,0:03:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也介紹女人給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適可而止 加利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.15,0:03:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一百五十三號的客人沒有還錢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狠狠地給他點顏色看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:04:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭登 待會再慢慢聽你說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也不要去剛才見面的女孩的學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.51,0:04:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛上頭的人是這麼命令的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.13,0:04:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭登 你到底幹什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想說的話就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.73,0:04:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 千萬別忘了這條命令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是在最底層 你也是組織的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上頭的命令是絕對的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.01,0:04:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惟有服從這一條才能在組織裡待下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會打架還想混飯吃的人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Millennion裡是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.61,0:04:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.70,0:04:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘這個機會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的老大Big Daddy創造了Millennion
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:04:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也包括了它的真諦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.69,0:05:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 遇見瑪麗亞了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 我就想會這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後還被組織給警告了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好想一想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 她住在Big Daddy的家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就意味著能和組織上頭接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一一個不慎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會讓想幹掉Big Daddy的敵對組織知道瑪麗亞的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會給Daddy帶來危險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.57,0:05:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才要防患於未然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.93,0:05:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事我早就瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我還是想告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換到我的立場上想想的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.72,0:05:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.17,0:05:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 哈利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.67,0:05:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.38,0:05:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是布蘭登·西特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打攪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 請你等一會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好極了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡垂釣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垂釣 就是釣魚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…一次也沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼跟我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:08:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 就這樣 讓誘餌像活的一樣去引魚兒上鉤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的資質不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾有一個可稱得上摯友的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經是十五年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人犯了罪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了補償所犯的罪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他收養了一個少女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他決定即使捨棄自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要撫養這位少女成人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使她不再生活在黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到一個充滿陽光的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.30,0:08:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但摯友的願望還沒達成就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我決定為了完成他的心願
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續收養那位少女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.56,0:08:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 布蘭登·西特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.47,0:09:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡 Big Daddy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想見她的話 到我的別墅來也沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.69,0:09:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不要再在其他地方再和她見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.99,0:09:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會盡全組織的力量來保護她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的家族
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不把你的魚竿提起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.46,0:09:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著 只顧用力的話線會斷的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順著它掙扎的方向來用力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 就是這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.18,0:09:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.34,0:10:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Daddy在這個城市 還只是沙漠和稀落的草地時
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就移民過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候比現在還要混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們紛爭不息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.16,0:10:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy為了保護鄰居和朋友而戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.15,0:10:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無關是與非 只為了生存下去而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後隨著鎮子的擴大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.04,0:10:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy要保護的也越來越多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護數十上百有如家人般的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy創建了組織 Millennion
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了守護
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 只是為了守護而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.36,0:10:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連續遲到的道歉就用這東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡只有男人在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:11:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼處理這東西啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.61,0:11:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 就交給我老媽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚到我家來吃晚飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大秘藏的波旁酒也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭登
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 沒想到布蘭登還有這種興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是不愛講話 但有了魚就不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.65,0:11:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨 我是執事時岡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.28,0:11:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很大的房子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.87,0:11:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最初也完全不習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭登 你現在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒干危險的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在工作 送貨的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道哈利也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 你們都好好在工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.43,0:12:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 就我一個住在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.10,0:12:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 學校畢業以後進公司工作的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.19,0:12:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想一個人生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想靠自己的力量來生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為你們在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是說要離開這兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才…叔叔…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說 要是連瑪麗亞都失去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓你一直呆在這兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來介紹 我的朋友布蘭登
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫淺蔥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:12:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫布蘭登·西特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭登嗎 今後瑪麗亞就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.67,0:13:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來我成電燈泡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.40,0:13:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我烤了派 想三個人一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要取消宴會？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 蘭迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"閃電"那邊的人好像開始行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:14:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從某方面得到的情報看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.95,0:15:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在打今晚宴會的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這次的宴會是Big Daddy的商界人士招待會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.27,0:15:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在中止的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,0:15:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但以防萬一還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宴會照原定計劃舉行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.05,0:15:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們只要去收集"閃電"的情報就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就交給我和我的部下來辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就交給你了 貝爾·沃肯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈利會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈利 鮑勃送來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.29,0:15:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先下手的好機會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管花多少錢都不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去收集"閃電"的情報去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.85,0:15:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣能參加嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:15:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.65,0:16:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭登
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服很適合你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.60,0:16:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那個頭髮有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.88,0:16:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.54,0:16:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我們去跳舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我教你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 我們公司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:16:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考慮以後以Millennion的事業為中心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.32,0:17:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你們建立更加密切的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.97,0:17:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標只是Millennion老大的人頭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.93,0:17:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要誤傷其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.95,0:17:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領路的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行得很順利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.45,0:17:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經有一個人潛入進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你擋道了 快滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.12,0:17:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 "閃電"的諸位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡開始禁止通行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.02,0:17:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Millennion！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好眼力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.65,0:18:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是"閃電"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.77,0:18:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前見過你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.86,0:18:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給了我一次很好的經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Millennion的哈利·麥克道韋爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.26,0:18:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打聽到了"閃電"要來襲擊的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.85,0:18:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就擅自行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.58,0:19:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想往上爬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.28,0:19:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 我先記下你們幹的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.20,0:19:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊回你們的老巢去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.65,0:19:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦屁股這種事就交給我們干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.46,0:20:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們公司也會誠心誠意地盡全力做好這個項目
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.79,0:20:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何也不會辜負您的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.30,0:20:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭登嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.85,0:20:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Daddy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.62,0:21:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭登
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堅持住 布蘭登
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.32,0:21:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個少年是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.13,0:21:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭迪 快叫救護車來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.78,0:21:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 把您留在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.06,0:21:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 請您一定要小心 Big Daddy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.89,0:21:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊 布蘭登
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.98,0:21:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼要保護我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.55,0:21:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了組織嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.61,0:22:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是為了瑪麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.39,0:22:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭登
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.18,0:22:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼舉槍 為什麼開槍 為什麼殺人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,0:22:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漸漸停滯的意識中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.13,0:22:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是浮現出了瑪麗亞和哈利的面孔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.53,0:22:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我一直在思考"守護"的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.14,0:24:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人默默地扣動了扳機
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.16,0:24:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火光又奪去了一個靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.45,0:24:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Millennion的布蘭登·西特
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.03,0:24:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為Sweeper的男人
